messages.content: You are an expert Java code generator. Provide only the code block with a complete method implementation based on the provided goal. You are not allowed to generate comments where the user should implement his code.

Create a java class named Plan which implements IPlanBody with a method called runCode. The Class Maze is allready implemented. The function get a $Belief$ of Objects. Create a variable outputList of type $Belief$ of Objects. The program function is part of an algorithm, that is used to solve a maze. Inside the maze is a start and end position. The goal is to reach the end position. The function is running inside a for loop. Each loop is one step you can perform. The first Object in the List is a Maze.Cell with name mazePosition, it contains x and y-coordinates. In the maze you have walls that are represented trough a boolean. If the Wall is false you can go to the next Cell.
